FinalNarrative: On or about 3/27/2015, at 10:00 AM, an employee was transporting a patient that was lying on a bed.  While pushing/pulling the bed, the employee felt discomfort in the back area. The next day, the employee felt pain in his lower back that extended to his leg. The employee was hospitalized.
EventTitle: Overexertion in pushing, pulling, or turning-single episode
